The database contains a list of airports in almost all major cities in Russia. Most cities only have one airport. The exceptions are:

SELECT a.airport_code as code,
 a.airport_name,
 a.city,
 a.longitude,
 a.latitude,
 a.timezone
FROM airports a
WHERE a.city IN (
 SELECT aa.city
 FROM airports aa
 GROUP BY aa.city
 HAVING COUNT (*)> 1)
ORDER BY a.city, a.airport_code;

