 Chelyabinsk      | CEK             | Chelyabinsk       | {1,2,3,4,5,6,7} | 01:50:00
 Rostov-on-Don    | ROV             | Rostov-on-Don     | {1,2,3,4,5,6,7} | 00:30:00
 Moscow           | VKO             | Vnukovo           | {1,2,3,4,5,6,7} | 01:10:00
 Cheboksary       | CSY             | Cheboksary        | {1,2,3,4,5,6,7} | 02:45:00
